Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.32,0:04:24.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼 這周也開始驗證…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.47,0:04:32.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所謂的約定…
